A derogatory term that roughly means ''rabble'' (although some translate it as ''riff-raff'' or ''dregs'').  Gained notoriety when used by French interior minister, [[Nicolas Sarkozy]], to describe the residents of crime-ridden neighborhoods.  His comment is widely attributed to causing the [[2005 Paris riots]] in France among the North African community there.

